name: ASOAW_V0.6
description: Trained for shaperwears, bikini, skirt, swimsuits and so on

modelVersions.name: V0.6
modelVersions.description:
This is my first serious workout.

It's not perfect, but it should be enough to keep using it :)

The model is based on v1.5 VAE.

This model was trained from almost 1800 individual images.

The focus here was on bodies and clothing.

Starting with tights, skirts, pantyhose, swimsuits, bikinis and other shaperwears.

The model can be used to exchange it with other faces, since no specific face has been trained and they sometimes look "weird".

The model was trained with sentences like:

"A picture of a ASOAW in a bikini, lies, shows the whole body from the front"
